# EPL critical lines

This is a webpage with a small widget to generate the critical lines of the
elliptical power law profile lens
[ADS](http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2015A%26A...580A..79T) -
[arXiv](http://arxiv.org/abs/1507.01819) -
[DOI](http://dx.doi.org/10.1051/0004-6361/201526773).

The page is accessible via [GitHub pages](http://ntessore.me/epl-critical-lines).
